<subSubSection pageId="1" pageNumber="592" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="1.[151,1436,1101,1738]" pageId="1" pageNumber="592">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,334,1677,1702]" pageId="1" pageNumber="592">Etymology.</emphasis>
The specific name is derived from Latin 
<emphasis box="[794,966,1678,1702]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="592">quadridigitatus</emphasis>
, referring to the four digitate processes of the gnathos.
</paragraph>
